---
// HolidayJoySection — repurposed as "Coming Home" full-bleed editorial CTA
---

<section class="coming-home">
  <div class="bg-image">
    <img src="/images/nella-1.jpg" alt="A Crown Palace Shih Tzu puppy in the golden hour" />
  </div>
  <div class="overlay"></div>

  <div class="coming-inner">
    <span class="kicker">Reserving Now · Spring &amp; Summer Litters</span>
    <h2 class="coming-title">
      The right shih tzu<br>
      is <em>waiting</em> for you.
    </h2>
    <p class="coming-lede">
      Our next wave of Shih Tzu puppies is already home with us — nursing, napping, and starting the first steps of early socialization. We place only a handful each season, and they go quickly to families we've had time to know.
    </p>
    <div class="coming-actions">
      <a href="/available-puppies" class="cta">
        View This Season's Puppies
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="/contact" class="cta-line">Start a Conversation</a>
    </div>

    <div class="signature">
      <span class="sig-swoosh"></span>
      <span>— raised, loved, and ready, The Crown Palace Shih Tzu Family</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .coming-home {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 620px;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .bg-image {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .bg-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 35%;
    filter: saturate(1.05) contrast(1.02);
  }

  .overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(100deg, rgba(43, 32, 24, 0.88) 0%, rgba(43, 32, 24, 0.55) 55%, rgba(43, 32, 24, 0.1) 100%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(31, 23, 18, 0.2) 0%, rgba(31, 23, 18, 0.55) 100%);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .coming-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 1280px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    background: rgba(212, 160, 85, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 160, 85, 0.4);
    padding: 0.55rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
  }

  .coming-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5.4vw, 4.8rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.02;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .coming-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .coming-lede {
    font-size: 1.12rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(251, 245, 233, 0.88);
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .coming-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem 1.25rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    background: var(--color-cream);
    color: var(--color-gray-900);
    padding: 1.1rem 1.9rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  }

  .cta:hover {
    background: var(--color-gold);
    color: var(--color-gray-900);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .cta svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta:hover svg { transform: translateX(3px); }

  .cta-line {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.1rem 0;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgba(251, 245, 233, 0.6);
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
  }

  .cta-line:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    border-color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .signature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    color: rgba(251, 245, 233, 0.75);
  }

  .sig-swoosh {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-gold);
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .coming-home { min-height: 540px; }
    .coming-inner { padding: 4rem 1.25rem; }
    .coming-lede { font-size: 1rem; }
    .cta { padding: 0.95rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.92rem; }
    .signature { font-size: 0.9rem; }
  }
</style>
